comment.author: 51979177@N02
comment._content: Definitely a job for Wonder Woman or Batman!!! I've been drawing blanks on all these (wonderful) portraits. A couple of possibilities - they might have been publicity shots of visiting JC WIlliamson stars (or something similar)...or perhaps they were visiting American tourists (a number of American cruises of the Pacific were evidently arranged in the 1920s...there are occasional reports and interviews with the tourists in the digitised newspapers)...my hunch is the pics were taken in the early 1920s...work in progress...
